    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/7cc3aa5238dfd15d9bd40003cb328603.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy items directly from customers, negotiate the best possible prices, and resell them with a pawn-style margin. Evaluate market value, spot opportunities, and trade <strong>over 180 unique</strong> products as you grow your pawn shop from a small hustle into a serious pawn trading business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/e436517472df5da7c5b88f606f90088f.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/e436517472df5da7c5b88f606f90088f.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/e436517472df5da7c5b88f606f90088f.mp4?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/0a9cf89054739d845cec68644554e637.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade over 180 different items, from furniture and appliances to all kinds of secondhand goods. Every day brings new deals and new chances to make profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean or repair selected products, negotiate with customers, buy low and sell smart. Every item is an opportunity to grow your pawnshop business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/80c8e095b5e6ad3eb0d48ff9013061fb.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your pawnshop exactly the way you want. Build walls, floors, ceilings, windows, and doors to create your perfect layout from scratch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tear down anything you no longer need and rebuild freely. Reshape your space anytime to fit expansions, upgrades, and your growing business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/fb0745d709e6c5706df21524e7c3b409.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/fb0745d709e6c5706df21524e7c3b409.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/fb0745d709e6c5706df21524e7c3b409.mp4?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/f9f5cfef7afa8742bfde3d18cf7462a4.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refresh your pawnshop with a full renovation system. Upgrade walls, floors, and ceilings to change the overall look of your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Renovation changes the shop’s appearance, giving you more control over how your space looks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/c9368880d9b4fd094825076ff1a5e3c6.mp4?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/09ac704db44686d288ca861f433f58b9.avif?t=1770386899\" width=950 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your old pawn shop to unlock new possibilities. Expand available space, improve shop functionality, and prepare your business for bigger deals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase product licenses to unlock new item categories and gain access to more valuable goods as your pawn empire grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/345e452ba1c0a9c8526e5b6bc4213069.poster.avif?t=1770386899\" width=1170 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/345e452ba1c0a9c8526e5b6bc4213069.webm?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149100/extras/345e452ba1c0a9c8526e5b6bc4213069.mp4?t=1770386899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
